Pre-check:

- [ ] Ensure dependencies are up-to-date: `mix deps.update --all`
- [ ] Run `mix credo --strict` to check for code complaints
- [ ] Run `mix formatter`, commit any changes
- [ ] Run integration tests locally: `mix test --include integration`

Tests:

- [ ] `travis.yml`: Ensure most recent 3 minor Elixir versions are supported.
- [ ] `travis.yml`: Ensure most recent 5 Elastic Search versions are supported.

Release:

- [ ] Bump version in `mix.exs`
- [ ] Commit to GitHub
- [ ] Create a tag for this release, push tag to GitHub
- [ ] Publish with `mix hex.publish`
- [ ] Writeup changelog in `CHANGELOG.md`
